column6: BIG TIME concludes for the biggest criminal in the Marvel Universe! FREE OSBORN! The former Green Goblin, Iron Patriot and war-criminal director of H.A.M.M.E.R. gets his day in the sun, as the atrocities of his top-secret incarceration are revealed. Norman Osborn stands poised to win the day...will the super villain walk free to plague the Marvel Universe again?
